01:06.540 --> 01:08.359
The story so far...

01:08.360 --> 01:12.239
<i>At Waterloo the war was won,
but George was lost.</i>

01:12.240 --> 01:14.589
<i>Survivors came home
with new babies,</i>

01:14.590 --> 01:16.179
<i>or new destinations.</i>

01:16.180 --> 01:18.119
<i>The regiment is under orders
for India.</i>

01:18.120 --> 01:20.879
<i>And Amelia had an offer
she had to refuse.</i>

01:20.880 --> 01:23.679
<i>I lost my husband.
I will not lose my son.</i>

01:23.680 --> 01:26.489
<i>Matilda took her revenge
from beyond the grave.</i>

01:26.490 --> 01:27.799
£100.

01:27.800 --> 01:30.119
You jumped the wrong way
there, Becky, my girl.

01:30.120 --> 01:33.199
<i>Undaunted, Becky came up with
her best plan yet...</i>

01:33.200 --> 01:36.599
This shall be our game room.
Here you will play all-comers
and all games.

01:36.600 --> 01:39.559
<i>..aiming straight
for her biggest prize.</i>

01:39.560 --> 01:43.919
Tonight, Becky works out
how to live well on nothing a year.

01:43.920 --> 01:46.559
It's easy!
It's Vanity Fair!

01:46.560 --> 01:49.249
A world where everyone
is striving...

01:49.250 --> 01:51.000
for what is not worth having.

